{"tid":2211314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"羅 12:19-21 把炭火堆在敵人頭上","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T05:33:54.000Z","uid":266243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9a783064e3aa454cf4c333b6874c8b7fdb1453","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"羅 12:19-21:<br />\n19 親愛的弟兄，不要自己伸冤，寧可讓步，聽憑主怒；因為經上記著：主說：伸冤在我；我必報應。<br />\n20 所以，你的仇敵若餓了，就給他吃，若渴了，就給他喝；因為你這樣行就是把炭火堆在他的頭上。<br />\n21 你不可為惡所勝，反要以善勝惡。<br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffa6f47d0bec487d3363226f184897808b5cf63","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"推呀，係愛呀"},{"pid":"29c89bf6aa297317c5c7cce3323c8267da49c302","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"愛可請求天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e26546eae711e142fba7850d67a43daa476b42","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"895ca5f16959ec3d1cd651aef38a2b395f2fa308","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"61bd77f9ae54b0676e18542c2f3a69f38db16cea","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"e55e1976143ea8f66ca7c43b1fe62f337818c840","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"左"},{"pid":"4ae271730c0664e7131bfb8fa73a3e85b0023a1c","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"膠"},{"pid":"cbad7d34ad6158cd1934fcca623969ed7122e9c3","tid":2211314,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2